# ⚖️ PART 10 — LOAD BALANCER

Distributes traffic across servers.

```
User
 │
 ▼
Load Balancer
 │
 ├─ EC2 #1
 ├─ EC2 #2
 └─ EC2 #3
```

Prevents server overload.

---

# 📈 PART 11 — AUTO SCALING

Automatically launches new servers.

```
High CPU
   ↓
Launch new EC2
```

Useful during:

* product launches
* flash sales
* viral traffic

